  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this randomized controlled study is to evaluate psychological variables,
      mindfulness, and pain in the context of a specialized yoga program for individuals with SCI.
      Participants will be randomized to either a wait-list control condition or to a specialized
      yoga program condition.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
